            <note xml:id="foot.f2"><hi rend="italic">The evolutionist at large</hi> comprised twenty-two essays that had originally appeared in a column in the <hi rend="italic">St James’s Gazette</hi> (<ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_11351.xml">Allen 1881</ref>, p. vii).</note>
